# HostelPro — Hostel Management System

A comprehensive MERN stack hostel management system for managing rooms, residents, billing, and maintenance.

## 🔗 Live Demo
- **Frontend:** https://hotelmanagmen.netlify.app
- **Backend API:** https://hotel-managment-agx7.onrender.com

## 🔑 Test Credentials
| Role | Email | Password |
|------|-------|----------|
| Admin | admin@hostelpro.com | admin123 |
| Staff | staff@hostelpro.com | staff123 |
| Resident | resident@hostelpro.com | res123 |

## ✨ Features
- JWT Authentication with role-based access control (Admin, Staff, Resident)
- Room Allocation with real-time floor grid view and room creation
- Resident Management with check-in/checkout, room changes, and a read-only profile view
- Maintenance Request tracking (residents see only their own; staff assign and update status)
- Billing and Invoice generation with discounts, late fees, and payment history
- Online payments via Razorpay, plus manual cash/UPI/bank recording
- Real-time in-app notifications for maintenance updates, new invoices, payments received, check-ins and check-outs
- Financial Reports with charts (admin only)
- User Role management and permissions

## 🔐 RBAC Permissions
| Feature | Admin | Staff | Resident |
|---------|-------|-------|----------|
| View all rooms | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Create/Edit rooms | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| View all residents | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| View own profile | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| All maintenance requests | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Own maintenance only | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| All invoices | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Own invoices only | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Financial reports | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| User management | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Reseed demo data | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |

## ⚠️ Known Limitations
- **SMS notifications** are not implemented — in-app and email notifications are live, but there's no SMS provider (e.g. Twilio) wired up yet.
- **Payment plans/installments** aren't supported yet — invoices are paid in full or via manual partial payments, but there's no way to schedule an invoice into multiple installments.
- **Room preference on assignment** — admins currently assign any vacant room manually; there's no field to capture a resident's preferred room type/floor.

## 🛡 Security
- Passwords are hashed with bcrypt; sessions use JWT (7-day expiry).
- All state-changing routes are protected by role-based middleware (`admin`/`staff`/`resident`).
- Public self-registration always creates a `resident` account — the API never trusts a client-supplied role.
- User listing, role changes, env checks, and the demo data seed routes are admin-only.
- CORS is restricted to known frontend origins (set via `FRONTEND_URL`), not `*`.
- Rate limiting is applied globally and more strictly on `/api/auth/login`.
- Security headers are set via `helmet`.

## 🛠 Tech Stack
| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React 18, Vite, TailwindCSS, Recharts |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas |
| Auth | JWT + bcrypt |
| Payments | Razorpay |
| Email | Nodemailer (Brevo SMTP) |
| Security | Helmet, express-rate-limit |
| Deployment | Netlify + Render |

## 🚀 Setup & Run Locally

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v18+
- MongoDB (local) or MongoDB Atlas account

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd server
npm install
# Create .env file with:
# MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/hostel-pro
# JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
# PORT=5000
# FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
# SMTP_USER=your_brevo_smtp_user
# SMTP_PASS=your_brevo_smtp_password
# SMTP_FROM=noreply@yourdomain.com
# RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_razorpay_key_secret
npm run dev
# Server runs on http://localhost:5000
```

### Frontend Setup
```bash
cd client
npm install
# Create .env file with:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
# VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id
npm run dev
# App runs on http://localhost:5173
```

### Seed Data
The seed routes wipe and recreate all demo data, so they require an admin login.

```bash
# 1. Log in as admin (admin@hostelpro.com / admin123), then in the browser
#    console run: localStorage.getItem('token')
# 2. Call the seed route with that token:
curl http://localhost:5000/api/auth/seed-all \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"
```

## 📁 Project Structure
```
hostel-pro/
├── server/
│   ├── models/        # Room, Resident, Invoice, Maintenance, Notification, User, Team
│   ├── routes/        # Auth, Rooms, Residents, Maintenance, Invoices, Reports, Notifications
│   ├── middleware/    # JWT auth + RBAC role check
│   ├── utils/          # Email (Nodemailer) + Notification helper
│   └── server.js
└── client/
    └── src/
        ├── pages/          # Dashboard, ResidentDashboard, Rooms, Residents, Billing, etc.
        ├── components/     # Layout, Sidebar, Topbar, AddResidentModal, ResidentProfileModal
        ├── context/        # Auth context
        └── api/            # Axios instance
```